                    <event ana="http://syriaca.org/keyword/letters http://syriaca.org/keyword/bishops http://syriaca.org/keyword/heresy http://syriaca.org/keyword/ordination http://syriaca.org/keyword/canon-law http://syriaca.org/keyword/priests http://syriaca.org/keyword/deacons http://syriaca.org/keyword/clergy http://syriaca.org/keyword/communion http://syriaca.org/keyword/anti-nestorian" notBefore="0513" notAfter="0518">
                        <desc>
